      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted RH index must agree with measured RH within 20% relative error across all validated operating points.",
      "rationale": "RH agreement ranges from 8% to 16% relative error across four bench test operating points. All within 20% acceptance criterion. Systematic over-prediction of RH observed at high-flow conditions, conservatively biasing safety assessment."
